---
title: Sheet Pan Chicken & Pepper Fajitas with Pico de Gallo, Monterey Jack & Lime Crema
description: Tonight’s meal is quick, easy, and downright delicious. It’s got it all—we’re talking spiced chicken, strips of green pepper, and sliced onion, all tossed on a baking sheet and roasted until tender and lightly charred. The joyous jumble is then piled into steamy flour tortillas along with fresh salsa, a drizzle of lime crema, and a sprinkle of Monterey Jack cheese. Talk about a fiesta on your plate!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/615db681c4d9f2725126da76-4a843d25.jpg
